                    <h4 class="my-3">Psilocybin Therapy</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">Psilocybin is an active ingredient in some species of mushrooms, often referred to as ‘magic mushrooms’. We’ve developed an investigational, synthesised formulation of psilocybin, called COMP360, and are researching its effectiveness for certain serious mental health disorders, including treatment-resistant depression, post-traumatic stress disorder, and anorexia nervosa.</p>
